<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure140>
    dc:description "Figure 140. Solanum radicans A flowering habit B fruiting habit C detail of adaxial leaf surface D detail of abaxial leaf surface E flower bud F dissected flower G fruit (A, D-F Knapp et al. 10267 B Knapp et al. 10416). Illustration by R. Wise." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897601" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure141>
    dc:description "Figure 141. Solanum radicans A habit B flowering branch C flowers at full anthesis with flower buds D maturing fruits (A Saerkinen et al. 4065 B Knapp et al. 10417 C Gonzales et al. 2877 D Knapp et al. 10304). Photos by S. Knapp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897602" ;
